<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.243643>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Lurymare clavocapitata n. sp., AM W. 44065, MI QLD 2351, AM W. 44692, MI QLD 2395. A. Live specimen; B – E. Histological sections of the reproductive system; F. Sagittal reconstruction of the reproductive system, anterior to the left in B – F. Abbreviations: cg = cement glands, fa = female atrium, i = intestine, ma = male atrium, pv = prostatic vesicle, s = stylet, spv = spermiducal vesicles, su = sucker, sv = seminal vesicle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/243643/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

